{"tid":1280474,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎良心警察做二五仔齊爆高層大鑊(有圖)","createTime":"2019-07-03T03:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T04:22:40.000Z","uid":63129,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a19d0776db214e704139f1265ad8b2ef73ad0d8","tid":1280474,"uid":63129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"其實100%警察都係衰 冇例外 <br />\n<br />\n因為個政府衰 佢揀嘅警察就會衰<br />\n就算人品係好 入去受嘅訓練都會衰<br />\n就算訓練係好 岀嚟接受嘅指令都會衰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一切禍害嘅來源都係來自港共政府</span><br />\n<br />\n日日屌 屌到散仔都想做二五仔攻擊上面爆大鑊<br />\n如果呢度仲有邊個警察良心發現<br />\n麻煩叫朋友又好 自己post又好<br />\n一定要將政府嘅惡行一一告知<br />\n<br />\n612行動會派年輕大陸人即時落嚟做鬼 <br />\n亦有啲入咗telegram group <br />\n所以麻煩監察下身邊人係咪香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zoGRPGW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzoGRPGW.png&h=01d5f2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyR2WmW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyR2WmW.png&h=3877a0c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察朋友感受<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BzKv5fh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBzKv5fh.png&h=fd94142a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpASy9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpASy9C.png&h=cfc9f4f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實抗爭者今日都想打死你地<br />\n係因曾經都渴望過 警察會企喺香港人嘅一邊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b3da7a01310ee7a2031f93a5f847582b4fb52f","tid":1280474,"uid":5499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"唔洗幫黑警洗白<br />\n黑警同TVB一樣無一個係無辜"},{"pid":"497404529c1a9cc3fa90751143409c3ef4a400c4","tid":1280474,"uid":63129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5b3da7a01310ee7a2031f93a5f847582b4fb52f","tid":1280474,"uid":5499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"cit